pageProjet.texte: In summary, we aim to promote youth-led climate action through partnership with local and international stakeholders in the fight against climate change and to ensure environmental sustainability. We provide a platform through which young climate activist can showcase their talents and skills by actively participating in major projects and programs geared towards achieving our goals.
